properties.Name: Bourbon Pub
properties.Notes: 2000, page 122: "Many of the gay bars are on or near Rampart, St. Ann and Dumaine streets in the vicinity of Armstrong Park. The neighborhoods around the park are not safe, so be very careful, and don't go into the park at night unless there's a major event."

properties.Name: Checkpoint Charlie's
properties.Notes: 2000: "The 1993 film The Pelican Brief included several scenes shot here."

properties.Name: Pravda
properties.Notes: "The beautiful back garden, surprising in its openness after the warmth and intimacy of the bar space, is said to be a reenactment of the primitivist spirit behind fantasies of collectivist social organization."
